# Cloudflare Pages rewrite rules — see https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# All NFC visit URLs (https://mingxinwang.com/nfc/{userCode}/) get rewritten
# to the landing page at /nfc/. We use status 200 (rewrite, not redirect)
# so the browser keeps the original URL in the address bar — the user
# taps the "打开异想盒" button on the landing page and iOS re-attempts
# the Universal Link with the full original URL preserved.
#
# Without this rewrite, /nfc/{userCode}/ would 404 because Hugo only
# has content at /nfc/, not at every possible userCode.
/nfc/*   /nfc/   200
/bind/*  /bind/  200